earning a smile from her. Julia is dropped into&nbsp;
a water tank before the curtains fall, hiding&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:14.080 --> 00:02:18.400
the tank from the audience's view. The curtains&nbsp;
rise, revealing Julia safely out of the tank.

