Borden insists that his knot is better. With&nbsp;
Borden gone, Cutter then scolds Angier for&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:43.680 --> 00:02:47.040
kissing Julia's legs on stage, which could&nbsp;
reveal to the audience that she's his wife.

