old to hide his props under baggy clothes and a&nbsp;
hunched posture. That evening, Angier tries the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:00.320 --> 00:03:04.000
trick Borden claimed but finds it difficult&nbsp;
to walk with a fishbowl under his clothes.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:08.960
Angier can't fathom the idea of living a lie, as&nbsp;
Borden assumed Chung Ling Soo does. Angier claims&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:08.960 --> 00:03:12.560
he only changed his name to spare his family&nbsp;
from embarrassment with his theatrical career.

00:03:13.200 --> 00:03:16.960
While assisting at a small show,&nbsp;
Borden meets Sarah and her nephew,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:16.960 --> 00:03:21.200
who cries for the bird that disappears in the&nbsp;
act. Even when the bird is magically returned,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:21.200 --> 00:03:25.520
the boy is convinced the original bird is dead.&nbsp;
After the show, Borden returns the living bird&nbsp;&nbsp;

