with the others. He opens the pedestal where&nbsp;
the first bird disappeared and was killed,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:29.200 --> 00:03:34.160
just as the boy said. He meets with Sarah and the&nbsp;
boy outside, praising the boy's perceptiveness.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:34.160 --> 00:03:38.000
After having lunch with them, Borden walks Sarah&nbsp;
to her apartment, but she refuses to let him in.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:38.560 --> 00:03:41.600
He leaves as she enters her home, only&nbsp;
to magically appear in her kitchen.

