the water tank where he drowned. The water tank's&nbsp;
trick lock was replaced by a real one, preventing&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:55.360
Angier's escape. This water tank, Cutter explains,&nbsp;
has a history with both Borden and Angier.

