for his first show. Sarah worries about their&nbsp;
finances, revealing that she's pregnant. Borden&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:46.480 --> 00:04:50.160
shares his bullet catch trick with Sarah, showing&nbsp;
that the bullet is not in the gun when fired.

