00:04:59.760 --> 00:05:03.920
not noticing the man putting another bullet&nbsp;
inside. The man is Angier, still grieving&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:03.920 --> 00:05:08.640
under his disguise. The tension stretches out with&nbsp;
Angier demanding which knot he tied his wife with.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:08.640 --> 00:05:12.320
Fallon attempts to take the gun from Angier,&nbsp;
but he accidentally pulls the trigger.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:12.320 --> 00:05:15.120
Borden is shot in the hand,&nbsp;
screaming in pain as Angier leaves.

