According to Borden's journal, he told Angier&nbsp;
the truth that night. Angier is enraged,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:23.280
still unconvinced that Borden doesn't know&nbsp;
which knot he used the night of Julia's death.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:23.840 --> 00:05:28.320
Days later, Sarah tends to Borden's wound, which&nbsp;
has barely healed. With two fingers missing,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:28.320 --> 00:05:31.760
he can't perform many tricks other than what he's&nbsp;
been keeping, the one he'll be remembered for.

00:05:32.640 --> 00:05:36.400
Meanwhile, Cutter and Angier work together,&nbsp;
gathering materials for their show and hiring&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:36.400 --> 00:05:40.880
Olivia Wenscombe as Angier's assistant.&nbsp;
Cutter invents a contraption that makes a&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:40.880 --> 00:05:44.400
dove disappear without harming the bird.&nbsp;
